					<h2>3. Third-Party Services</h2>
					<p>We use the following third-party services that may process your data:</p>

					<table>
						<thead>
							<tr>
								<th>Service</th>
								<th>Purpose</th>
								<th>Policy</th>
							</tr>
						</thead>
						<tbody>
							<tr>
								<td>Google Analytics</td>
								<td>Site analytics and usage data</td>
								<td><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Privacy</a></td>
							</tr>
							<tr>
								<td>Google Tag Manager</td>
								<td>Script management (off main thread)</td>
								<td><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Privacy</a></td>
							</tr>
							<tr>
								<td>Cloudflare</td>
								<td>CDN, DNS, security (Turnstile CAPTCHA)</td>
								<td><a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Privacy</a></td>
							</tr>
							<tr>
								<td>Resend</td>
								<td>Email delivery for form submissions</td>
